✅ OPTION 1: Run it normally (RECOMMENDED)
Vite/React apps do not run inside XAMPP directly — they run using Node.js.
✔️ Steps:
1. Install Node.js
Download & install Node.js (LTS):
https://nodejs.org


terminal/command prompt to verify if nodejs is install bash

node -v
npm -v

after that locate your program folder 

cd "C:\xampp\htdocs\receipt

install dependencies

npm install

now to start a vite dev server / bash

npm run dev

it will give me a url like this http://localhost:5173/

then i will open it in my browser 
